WEBVTT

00:00.167 --> 00:02.167
Previously on Greenleaf.

00:05.007 --> 00:06.491
Did you sleep with Grace?

00:07.838 --> 00:10.326
I didn't say anything.

00:10.351 --> 00:12.010
You didn't have to!
You deserve each other.

00:12.045 --> 00:14.249
I don't want to marry Grace.
I want to marry you.

00:14.283 --> 00:17.260
You can tell everyone at the
mansion the wedding's off.

00:17.285 --> 00:19.264
These people aren't my problem anymore.

00:19.298 --> 00:20.344
You were going to just leave?

00:20.465 --> 00:21.799
I was trying to give you two some space.

00:21.833 --> 00:23.529
There is no "us two" anymore.

00:23.564 --> 00:24.735
<i>The wedding's off.</i>

00:24.770 --> 00:26.369
Woman on speaker:
<i>And then what happened?</i>

00:26.403 --> 00:29.273
He held me down. I couldn't breathe.

00:29.308 --> 00:32.209
<i>I begged him not to do it.
He wouldn't stop.</i>

00:32.244 --> 00:33.778
- Turn it off.
- She was just about to say

00:33.812 --> 00:35.087
exactly how Mac violated her.

00:35.122 --> 00:36.726
I don't need any more evidence.

00:36.760 --> 00:38.683
I want to hear his side of all this.

00:38.717 --> 00:41.118
I will not have him tried in absentia.

00:41.153 --> 00:44.221
And your blind spot
when it comes to this girl

00:44.256 --> 00:48.931
will be your undoing,
you mark my word, James.

00:48.965 --> 00:51.028
Mae wasn't able to convince you.

00:51.062 --> 00:52.756
You didn't convince her.

00:52.790 --> 00:58.436
- I never touched her.
- Stop lying! Now!

